        "subject": "LU-1259 mgs: avoid cancelling IR lock twice",
        "message": "LU-1259 mgs: avoid cancelling IR lock twice\n\nThere is a race that if IR shared lock is revoked fastly the\ncompletion ast can be called twice with the lock granted. The\nIR lock should be cancelled only once in this case.\n\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ia0cfde194126937f45e16777cf955b0a055a36e4\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_2"
    }
